g revision previews. When enabled, revision shortlinks will render the revision content directly for logged-out visitors instead of redirecting to the preview URL.'=>'默认情况下，PublishPress Revisions 阻止访客查看修订预览。当启用时，修订短链接将直接为未登录访客呈现修订内容，而不是重定向到预览 URL。','Dummy'=>'虚拟','No post types configured yet. Click "Add Post Type" to get started.'=>'尚未配置任何帖子类型。单击“添加帖子类型”开始。','Add Post Type'=>'添加帖子类型','Log entry deleted successfully.'=>'日志条目已成功删除。','%d log entries deleted successfully.'=>'%d 条日志条目已成功删除。','All logs have been cleared.'=>'所有日志已被清除。','Title'=>'标题','Details'=>'详细信息','Are you sure you want to delete this log entry?'=>'您确定要删除此日志条目吗？','Tablet'=>'平板电脑','Mobile'=>'移动设备','Desktop'=>'桌面','%1$s from %2$s visited at %3$s'=>'%1$s 来自 %2$s 于 %3$s 访问','%1$s visited at %2$s'=>'%1$s 于 %2$s 访问','From %1$s, visited at %2$s'=>'来自 %1$s，访问时间为 %2$s','Visited at %s'=>'访问时间 %s','via %s'=>'通过 %s','Edit shortlink settings'=>'编辑短链接设置','This post is in {status} status. It will become visible to the public on {date}.'=>'此帖子处于 {status} 状态。它将在 {date} 对公众可见。','Target url not found.'=>'未找到目标网址。','Invalid URL scheme. Only http, https, ftp, ftps, and mailto are allowed.'=>'无效的 URL 方案。仅允许 http、https、ftp、ftps 和 mailto。','Tiny slug could not created.'=>'无法创建小 slug。','Shortlink will appear here'=>'短链接将在这里显示','Enter a long URL and make a shortlink'=>'输入一个长URL并生成短链接','Long URL'=>'长网址','Create Shortlink'=>'创建短链接','Reset Today\'s Analytics'=>'重置今天的分析','Reset Week\'s Analytics'=>'重置本周的分析','Reset Month\'s Analytics'=>'重置本月的分析','Reset Year\'s Analytics'=>'重置今年的分析','Are you sure you want to reset the analytics for this period? This action cannot be undone.'=>'您确定要重置此期间的分析吗？此操作无法撤销。','Today'=>'今天','Last 7 Days'=>'过去 7 天','Last 1 Month'=>'过去 1 个月','Last 1 Year'=>'过去 1 年','If you like %1$s please leave us a %2$s rating. Thank you!'=>'如果您喜欢 %1$s，请给我们留下一个 %2$s 评分。谢谢！','About'=>'关于','Documentation'=>'文档','Contact'=>'联系','Download QR Code'=>'下载二维码','We have developed extensions for the below browsers.'=>'我们已为以下浏览器开发了扩展。','C